trans-unit.source: Represents the method that handles post-cache substitution.
trans-unit.target: Representerer metoden som behandler etter hurtigbufferen erstatning.

trans-unit.source: The HttpResponseSubstitutionCallback delegate, in combination with the <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.WriteSubstitution%2A> method, is used for rendering post-cache content for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator> controls.
trans-unit.target: I kombinasjon med representanten med HttpResponseSubstitutionCallback den <xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.WriteSubstitution%2A>metoden brukes til gjengivelse innhold etter hurtigbufferen for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator>Kontroller.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> </xref:System.Web.HttpResponse.WriteSubstitution%2A>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> control, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution.MethodName%2A> property to specify the name of the callback method to invoke when the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> control executes.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>kontrollere ved å bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution.MethodName%2A>til å angi navnet på tilbakeringing-metode for å aktivere når den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>kontrollen kjører.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution.MethodName%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>

trans-unit.source: The callback method that you specify must be a static method on the page or on the user control that contains the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden tilbakeringing som du angir må være en statisk metode på siden eller brukerkontrollen som inneholder den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Substitution>

trans-unit.source: The signature for the callback method must match the signature for an HttpResponseSubstitutionCallback delegate that takes an <xref:System.Web.HttpContext> parameter and returns a string.
trans-unit.target: Signaturen for metoden tilbakeringing må samsvare med signaturen for en med HttpResponseSubstitutionCallback representant som tar en <xref:System.Web.HttpContext>parameteren og returnerer en streng.</xref:System.Web.HttpContext>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator> control, rendering is independent of the page caching unless an event handler is provided for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated> event.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator>kontroll, gjengivelse er uavhengig av side-hurtigbufring, med mindre en hendelsesbehandling er angitt for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated>hendelsen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator>

trans-unit.source: If no <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated> event handler is present, post-cache substitution is used to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator> content.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated>hendelsesbehandlingen, etter hurtigbufferen erstatning brukes til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator>innhold.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.AdRotator.AdCreated>
